statements: INSERT INTO MusicTheoryExercises(exercise_id, exercise_topic, difficulty_level, question, correct_answer, explanation) VALUES(1, 'Note Identification', 'Beginner', 'What is the note on the third line of the treble clef?', 'C', 'The note on the third line of the treble clef is C.');

INSERT INTO MusicTheoryExercises(exercise_id, exercise_topic, difficulty_level, question, correct_answer, explanation) VALUES(2, 'Chord Progressions', 'Intermediate', 'What is the most common chord progression in pop music?', 'I-IV-V-I', 'The most common chord progression in pop music is I-IV-V-I.');

INSERT INTO MusicTheoryExercises(exercise_id, exercise_topic, difficulty_level, question, correct_answer, explanation) VALUES(3, 'Scales', 'Advanced', 'What is the relative minor key of C major?', 'A minor', 'The relative minor key of C major is A minor.');

INSERT INTO MusicTheoryExercises(exercise_id, exercise_topic, difficulty_level, question, correct_answer, explanation) VALUES(4, 'Rhythm Patterns', 'Intermediate', 'What type of note receives half the value of a whole note?', 'Half note', 'A half note receives half the value of a whole note.');

INSERT INTO MusicTheoryExercises(exercise_id, exercise_topic, difficulty_level, question, correct_answer, explanation) VALUES(5, 'Intervals', 'Beginner', 'What is the interval between C and E in a major scale?', 'Major third', 'The interval between C and E in a major scale is a major third.');

INSERT INTO MusicTheoryExercises(exercise_id, exercise_topic, difficulty_level, question, correct_answer, explanation) VALUES (1, 'Interval Identification', 'Intermediate', 'What is the interval between C and E?', 'Major 3rd', 'A Major 3rd consists of 4 half steps.');

INSERT INTO MusicTheoryExercises(exercise_id, exercise_topic, difficulty_level, question, correct_answer, explanation) VALUES (2, 'Chord Progressions', 'Advanced', 'Identify the progression: Cmaj7 - G7 - Cmaj7', 'I - V7 - I', 'This is a typical tonic to dominant to tonic progression.');

INSERT INTO MusicTheoryExercises(exercise_id, exercise_topic, difficulty_level, question, correct_answer, explanation) VALUES (3, 'Sight Reading', 'Beginner', 'What note is one space above the staff?', 'F', 'The note one space above the staff is F.');

INSERT INTO MusicTheoryExercises(exercise_id, exercise_topic, difficulty_level, question, correct_answer, explanation) VALUES (4, 'Ear Training', 'Intermediate', 'Identify the played chord: A minor', 'A C E', 'The A minor chord consists of A, C, and E notes.');

INSERT INTO MusicTheoryExercises(exercise_id, exercise_topic, difficulty_level, question, correct_answer, explanation) VALUES (5, 'Harmonic Analysis', 'Advanced', 'Analyze the chord progression: Dm7 - G7 - Cmaj7', 'ii7 - V7 - IMaj7', 'This progression follows the ii - V7 - I pattern in the key of C major.');
